    public class TwitterSource
extends org.apache.flink.streaming.api.functions.source.RichSourceFunction<String>
implements org.apache.flink.api.common.functions.StoppableFunction
    Implementation of SourceFunction specialized to emit tweets from Twitter. This is not a parallel source because the Twitter API only allows two concurrent connections.
